{"tid":2004811,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台：四月氣溫較正常低0.6度、最高30.3度、雨量少約55%","createTime":"2020-05-06T16:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T12:22:55.000Z","uid":7439,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f564386e89acb64dc6342d377a019de6eafe83b7","tid":2004811,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T16:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200506/_2020050606472122788.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200506%2F_2020050606472122788.jpg&h=cf6d9aed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202005/05/P2020050500350.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202005%2F05%2FP2020050500350.htm&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBXs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=d457850b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202005/05/P2020050500350.htm</a><br />\n較涼及少雨的四月<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  由於影響華南的東北季候風較正常強，二○二○年四月本港較正常稍涼。本<span style=\"color: red;\">月平均氣溫為22.0度，較正常值22.6度低0.6度。</span>另外，由於影響華南大氣低層的偏南氣流較弱及水氣較少，本月較正常少雨。<span style=\"color: red;\">全月錄得的雨量為77.8毫米，較正常值174.7毫米少約百分之五十五。</span>本年首四個月的累積雨量為213.7毫米，較同期正常值336.1毫米少約百分之三十六。<br />\n   <br />\n  受東北季候風及隨後清勁至強風程度的偏東氣流影響，四月一日至四日本港多雲及有幾陣雨。在東風增強及高空擾動影響下，四月五日及六日本港天氣轉涼及驟雨較多。本港各區在這兩日普遍錄得超過20毫米雨量，而新界部分地區更錄得超過40毫米雨量。在有雨的情況下，<span style=\"color: red;\">四月六日香港天文台錄得的氣溫下降至本月最低的16.1度。</span><br />\n   <br />\n  隨着高空擾動遠離，四月七日本港雨勢逐漸減弱，日間天色明朗。受較乾燥的偏東氣流及一道高壓脊影響，覆蓋本港的雲層轉薄，其後數日本港天氣普遍天晴及乾燥。隨着一道冷鋒移近，四月十一日本港雲量增多。該道冷鋒於四月十一日晚間橫過廣東沿岸地區並為該區帶來驟雨，本港各區錄得超過10毫米雨量。受冷鋒後的大陸氣流影響，四月十二日及十三日本港轉為天晴及非常乾燥，早上天氣清涼。<span style=\"color: red;\">四月十三日日間的相對濕度更一度下降至百分之三十以下。</span><br />\n   <br />\n  四月十四日本港大致多雲。受一道高壓脊影響，四月十五日及其後兩日本港天氣持續晴朗。受一股海洋氣流影響，四月十八日至二十一日本港日間大致天晴及炎熱，四月十九日及二十一日早上本港沿岸有霧。<br />\n   <br />\n  一道冷鋒於四月二十二日早上橫過廣東沿岸。受東北季候風及高空擾動影響，<span style=\"color: red;\">四月二十二日本港多雲及有雨，當日將軍澳及港島東區分別錄得超過40毫米雨量。其後三日本港天氣轉涼，持續多雲及有幾陣雨。</span>隨着東北季候風緩和，四月二十六日及二十七日本港部分時間有陽光，氣溫逐漸回升。在微風的情況下，這兩日本港日間有煙霞，四月二十六日赤鱲角的能見度曾下降至約3 000米。受一股大陸氣流影響，本港天氣持續好轉，四月二十八日本港普遍天晴及乾燥。受高空反氣旋影響，本月最後兩日本港天氣持續普遍天晴。在日間陽光充沛的情況下，<span style=\"color: red;\">四月三十日香港天文台錄得的最高氣溫上升至<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">本月最高的30.3度。</span></span><br />\n   <br />\n2020年5月5日（星期二）<br />\n香港時間12時35分"},{"pid":"830f78254704f5e5328956fa147efbf988fec16a","tid":2004811,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T16:30:14.000Z","msg":"四月唯一一樣高<br />\n<br />\n平均日最高氣溫 25.1 oC <br />\n比正常﹝長期平均﹞高 0.1 oC"},{"pid":"ead5d31f69d8d413a141abc10ab93295dbf14e3b","tid":2004811,"uid":7439,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T16:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200502/_2020050217523775730.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200502%2F_2020050217523775730.jpg&h=59b27e36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200502/_2020050217523911161.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200502%2F_2020050217523911161.jpg&h=77939172&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfccb45c490c6410588fac50662568ae47912df3","tid":2004811,"uid":7439,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T16:32:23.000Z","msg":"有罩就是好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200502/_2020050217524130288.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200502%2F_2020050217524130288.jpg&h=5952d23a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200506/_2020050612285014578.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200506%2F_2020050612285014578.jpg&h=a812d5a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a085e994938b4bfd4493e681bb998057edf56dd","tid":2004811,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T16:34:04.000Z","msg":"天文台：異常溫暖及少雨的三月<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1959135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1959135</a><br />\n<br />\n和暖多雨的二月(2019/20冬季平均最高氣溫為有記錄以來最高)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1909862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1909862</a><br />\n<br />\n天文台：有記錄以來最暖的一月<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1861875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1861875</a><br />\n<br />\n二○一九年為香港有記錄以來最暖的一年<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1816578\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1816578</a>"},{"pid":"254e2c95f27ab14587e1e2dcf097e3fc93c9e31c","tid":2004811,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T16:35:46.000Z","msg":"30度都話較正常低。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d608b70c527907dc07e290453d66a08a103a95b3","tid":2004811,"uid":7439,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T16:35:58.000Z","msg":"暖化撚反CUP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港天文台 HKO<br />\n10小時 &middot; <br />\n上月的全球平均溫度，與2016年4月並列為有記錄以來4月最高。其中歐亞大陸中部和北部、格陵蘭以及南極洲部分地區，顯著較正常溫暖。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/96094895_10157803915091888_3947984004916969472_o.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_sid=2d5d41&amp;_nc_ohc=IzGxp18JdmwAX_tFL0n&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=6f43520a623a5cbe377d666de1d0a162&amp;oe=5ED9564D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2