score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T16:35:46.000Z","msg":"30度都話較正常低。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T16:43:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4433094/org/6be5d4da66a8816508a2b9d18a767f33.jpg/rXuUaovqufP4upACm9h-0QzfKqlg8WlMUbsb5FG7G-Q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4433094%2Forg%2F6be5d4da66a8816508a2b9d18a767f33.jpg%2FrXuUaovqufP4upACm9h-0QzfKqlg8WlMUbsb5FG7G-Q&h=8ab14ff0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T06:37:09.000Z","msg":"預告：有雨<br />\n現實：酷熱天氣警告已發出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088015caabc456bc06323f69c05a054fc9c1b671","tid":2004811,"uid":127447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T06:38:04.000Z","msg":"暖化撚出嚟講幾句！"}],"pinned":{"pid":"a20eaae986c16a7115f504343d50987e8f5ac92b","tid":2004811,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:36:44.000Z","msg":"異常炎熱的五月<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  二○二○年五月上半月天氣普遍天晴炎熱，而下半月的天氣開始轉趨不穩定，間中有大驟雨。總括來說，本月遠較正常炎熱，平均最低氣溫為25.9度，較正常值高1.8度，是有紀錄以來五月的其中一個第二高。<span style=\"color: red;\">本月平均氣溫為27.7度，平均最高氣溫為30.4度，分別較其正常值高1.8度及2.0度，兩者皆是有紀錄以來五月的第五高。</span>此外，二○二○年三月至五月的春季亦異常溫暖，其間的平均最低氣溫、平均氣溫及平均最高氣溫為21.9度、23.7度及26.4度，分別是同期的第四高、第五高及第六高。本月亦較正常多雨，<span style=\"color: red;\">全月錄得的雨量為352.5毫米，較正常值304.7毫米多約百分之十六。</span>本年首五個月的累積雨量為566.2毫米，較同期正常值640.8毫米少約百分之十二。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200612/photo/bkn-20200612080216350-0612_00822_001_01b.jpg?20200612142454\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200612080216350-0612_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20200612142454&h=390510ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image2.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/3df71ab808a7f2af0f6a0df2789d37d5/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200612/_2020061213580548622.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F3df71ab808a7f2af0f6a0df2789d37d5%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200612%2F_2020061213580548622.jpg&h=f07d5339&s={SIZE}\" />"}}